responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3660A14A4834EB77A49514942B9C76BC", "Worse than the wretched goblins? Most of those beasts didn\'t speak, just babbled a name over and over, \"Rhebdo!\" But the dead, by my essence those goblins are meddling with reviving ancient corpses! As I watched the goblins\' leader communed with them in the dark down there. Then left them to shamble when he was through with his questioning.")
